doc: Reading annotation cache for @Sensio\Bundle\FrameworkExtraBundle\Configuration\Route annotation fails
Reading a cached `Sensio\Bundle\FrameworkExtraBundle\Configuration\Route` annotation fails with
Attempted to call an undefined method named "__set_state" of class "Sensio\Bundle\FrameworkExtraBundle\Configuration\Route"

since the annotation cache has been switched to a `Doctrine\Common\Cache\PhpFileCache` instance. This happened with commit [ca69fa340c97e5ffc3287ca4e4c4574690dc2847](https://github.com/symfony/symfony/commit/ca69fa340c97e5ffc3287ca4e4c4574690dc2847) but may be a merge conflict.
